        {
            "title": "三一國際澄清未來3年目標未必一定達成 不構成盈利預測",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">三一國際(00631)發公告，表示已注意若干媒體對公司未來3年目標的報道；公司聲明，有關數字是3年的目標，未必一定達成。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：三一國際官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240517_FI_source-web_00631.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：三一國際官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240517_FI_source-web_00631.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：三一國際官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">根據報道，三一國際已制一個於2027年實現收入500億元人民幣、毛利率增至24%的目標，又指該公司有信心於未來數年海外礦山裝備的複合增長將達20%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">三一國際澄清，上述數字是目標，未必一定能達成，聲明並不構成盈利預測。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14827411-%e4%b8%89%e4%b8%80%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b%e6%be%84%e6%b8%85%e6%9c%aa%e4%be%863%e5%b9%b4%e7%9b%ae%e6%a8%99%e6%9c%aa%e5%bf%85%e4%b8%80%e5%ae%9a%e9%81%94%e6%88%90-%e4%b8%8d%e6%a7%8b%e6%88%90%e7%9b%88%e5%88%a9",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20241031_FI_source-web_00631-704.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-03 12:30:56",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "半日收市｜港股收趺366點穿23000關   出口及手機股急瀉",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國公布對等關稅細則，港股早段曾挫564點，半日收跌366點跌穿23000關，惟仍跑跑贏區內股市，出口股及手機設備股急瀉。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股2.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股2.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數半日報22835點，跌366點或1.58%，跑贏區內股市，今早開市報22638點，跌564點或2.43%。最低見22638點，瀉564點或2.43%，隨即跌幅收窄，中段最高見22998，跌204點或0.88%，為上午高位。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數半日報5306點，跌120點或2.22%，今早開報5257點，跌168點或3.11%；</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生國企指數半日報8408，跌122點或1.44%，今早以8312點開市，跌219點或2.57%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指半日報22821，跌388點或1.67%，低水15點 ; 科指期貨半日報5304點，跌125點或2.3%，低水2點 ; 國指期貨半日報8408點，跌131點或1.54%，低水17點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交1639.71億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國在美股收市後公布對等關稅細則，向中國徵收34%關稅，大市早段顯著下挫，其後公布3月財新中國服務業PMI進一步升至51.9，高於市場預期的51.5，擴張速度為近3個月來高位，大市跌勢稍收歛。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">出口股大挫，申洲國際(02313)瀉13.82%，報53.3元，成交入20大 ; 創科實業(00669)插 10.82%，報83.65元，跌幅居藍籌股首二位。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"申洲國際官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1119x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/02313_WEB_1200.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"申洲國際官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1119x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/02313_WEB_1200.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">申洲國際官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">手機設備股亦捱沽，比亞迪電子(00285)挫8.49%，報37.2元 ; 舜宇光學(02382)跌7.17%，報69.25元; 瑞聲科技(02018)插14.66%，報40.45元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">龍頭科網股成跌市元兇，阿里巴巴(09988)跌5.15%，報123.3元 ; 騰訊(00700)跌1.83%，報494.8元 ; 京東(09618)挫4.88%，報154元。 </p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"阿里巴巴官網圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/bplib_20240215-150532_20231207_FI_source-web_阿里巴巴_source-web__704px.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"阿里巴巴官網圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/bplib_20240215-150532_20231207_FI_source-web_阿里巴巴_source-web__704px.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">阿里巴巴官網圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">聯想集團(00992)跌7.51%，報9.86元。     </p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內房向好，華潤置地(01109)升2.9%，報26.6元，為表現最佳藍籌股; 華潤萬象(01209)升1.57%，報35.5元 ; 中海外(00688)升0.89%，報13.54元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">晶片股跑贏，中芯國際(00981)升1.34%，報45.3元 ; 華虹半導體(01347)升0.32%，報31.55元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：華潤置地官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20230724_FI_source-web_01109-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：華潤置地官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20230724_FI_source-web_01109-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：華潤置地官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14827406-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%bd%9c%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e6%94%b6%e8%b6%ba366%e9%bb%9e%e7%a9%bf23000%e9%97%9c-%e5%87%ba%e5%8f%a3%e5%8f%8a%e6%89%8b%e6%a9%9f%e8%82%a1%e6%80%a5%e7%80%89",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/HKSTOCK_MIDDAY_source-licensed_fb.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-03 12:25:48",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "英皇澄天再錄成交  一房單位成交價513萬",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=14826001&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 80px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英皇地產港島南現樓臨海住宅項目「澄天」高層海景戶推售，今再錄得投資客入市，成交單位為一房的25樓B室，成交價513萬，實用面積287平方呎，成交呎價17875。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">買家為外區投資者，特別鍾情項目擁開揚海景景致，加上有見租金回報較銀行定存吸引，租金走勢持續向上，故購入單位作長綫收租用途。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">「澄天」至今已售出98伙，佔整體項目近9成，合共套現逾港幣6億。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14826001-%e8%8b%b1%e7%9a%87%e6%be%84%e5%a4%a9%e5%86%8d%e9%8c%84%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4-%e4%b8%80%e6%88%bf%e5%96%ae%e4%bd%8d%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4%e5%83%b9513%e8%90%ac",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/pp_emperor_bp_fb.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-03 12:10:48",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "3月送交註冊住宅樓宇買賣合約按月升近70%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=14825324&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 80px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">土地註冊處公布，3月送交註冊的所有種類樓宇買賣合約共6661份，按月升54.7%，按年升32.9%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上述交易涉及買賣合約總值456億元，按月升61.4%，按年升22.1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">3月住宅樓宇買賣合約佔5367份，按月升67.7%，按年升35.2%，總值388億元，按月升68.7%，按年升29.1%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14825324-3%e6%9c%88%e9%80%81%e4%ba%a4%e8%a8%bb%e5%86%8a%e4%bd%8f%e5%ae%85%e6%a8%93%e5%ae%87%e8%b2%b7%e8%b3%a3%e5%90%88%e7%b4%84%e6%8c%89%e6%9c%88%e5%8d%87%e8%bf%9170-2",
